article.description: — Landon Glasper had 27 points in N.C. A&T's 76-69 victory against William & Mary on Saturday.
article.headline: Glasper's 27 lead N.C. A&T past William & Mary 76-69
article.linkText: Glasper's 27 lead N.C. A&T past William & Mary 76-69
article.story: GREENSBORO, N.C. -- — Landon Glasper had 27 points in N.C. A&T's 76-69 victory against William & Mary on Saturday. Glasper had eight rebounds for the Aggies (6-13, 4-2 Coastal Athletic Association). Camian Shell added 15 points while going 3 of 5 and 8 of 10 from the free throw line, and also had nine rebounds. The Tribe (7-12, 2-4) were led in scoring by Chase Lowe, who finished with 25 points and seven rebounds. Trey Moss added 17 points and eight rebounds for William & Mary. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
